{"slug": "banish", "root": "banish", "category": "act", "gloss": "to drive out by power", "definition": "To banish is to drive a being out and forbid its return — a spirit to the infernal regions, a person from the realm, a demon from a body. It differs from a mere summoning-in-reverse: banishment carries the force of proclamation and prohibition, an expulsion declared as much as enacted, closing the door behind what it casts out.", "history": "The word comes through Old French *banir* from Frankish *bannjan*, 'to proclaim, to summon by ban' — the same *bann* behind 'ban' and the marriage 'banns,' so exile began as a public shout of expulsion. The turn is that this civic proclamation became a ritual one: what a court did to an outlaw, the exorcist and magician did to spirits. Crowley's Goetia describes the old gods 'banished to the infernal regions' by a new order; monks banished demons by invoking Mary or making the cross. From decree to dispelling, the sense holds. Magic uses *Banish* as a keyword — removing a permanent from the game, sometimes for good.", "def_sources": [{"label": "Crowley et al., Illustrated Goetia (gods banished to the infernal regions)", "where": "Medieval magic (PDF)"}, {"label": "Hanegraaff et al., Hermes Explains (banishing demons by invocation)", "where": "Renaissance magic (PDF)"}, {"label": "Etymonline, s.v. banish", "where": "Etymology reference"}], "is_keyword": false, "etymology": {"lang": "Germanic", "origin": "Old French banir, from Frankish *bannjan 'to proclaim, summon by ban'", "first": "late 14c.", "note": "Same *bann as 'ban' and the marriage 'banns' — banishment was a public proclamation of expulsion, a shout as much as an act.", "hook": "Exile as a public shout."}, "essay": null, "sources": ["Etymonline (Douglas Harper)", "Wiktionary", "classical lexica (Lewis & Short, LSJ, Bosworth–Toller)", "Ted's historical-magic DBs (WitchcraftStudiesDB, AgrippaDOP, MedievalMagicDB)"], "stats": {"flavor_total": 15, "oracle_total": 1, "in_flavor_cards": 15, "in_oracle_cards": 1, "name_match_count": 13, "by_variant": {"banished": 8, "banish": 4, "banishment": 2, "banishes": 1, "banishing": 1}, "first_year": 1997, "colors": {"W": 16, "B": 6, "U": 3, "G": 3, "C": 4, "R": 1}, "by_year": {"1997": 1, "2003": 1, "2008": 2, "2009": 2, "2011": 1, "2015": 2, "2018": 1, "2019": 2, "2020": 2, "2021": 1, "2022": 5, "2023": 2, "2024": 2, "2025": 4, "2026": 1}}, "cards": [{"id": "1f18e63d-ab1f-426c-afd5-ce89433394ca", "name": "Banish into Fable", "set": "ELD", "type_line": "Instant", "rarity": "rare", "colors": ["U", "W"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/2/b/2b5e4c5d-7d1d-4426-8351-35c12e29d9c3.jpg?1782707716", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/2/b/2b5e4c5d-7d1d-4426-8351-35c12e29d9c3.jpg?1782707716", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/eld/325/banish-into-fable?utm_source=api", "local": "img/banish/1f18e63d-ab1f-426c-afd5-ce89433394ca.jpg"}, {"id": "ae6ef097-bd52-4bf8-81a8-2e6c643fc805", "name": "Banish to Another Universe", "set": "WHO", "type_line": "Enchantment", "rarity": "uncommon", "colors": ["W"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/6/1/61f39d4c-af2d-486d-9408-b987474f8352.jpg?1782696179", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/6/1/61f39d4c-af2d-486d-9408-b987474f8352.jpg?1782696179", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/who/13/banish-to-another-universe?utm_source=api", "local": "img/banish/ae6ef097-bd52-4bf8-81a8-2e6c643fc805.jpg"}, {"id": "2800830c-73c6-4097-be7b-d698c6813c38", "name": "Banishing Slash", "set": "NEO", "type_line": "Sorcery", "rarity": "uncommon", "colors": ["W"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/e/4/e4b8946b-6604-49ca-98db-18a540b1b4e5.jpg?1782702329", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/e/4/e4b8946b-6604-49ca-98db-18a540b1b4e5.jpg?1782702329", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/neo/3/banishing-slash?utm_source=api", "local": "img/banish/2800830c-73c6-4097-be7b