67-b47e-f44318fc93b2.jpg?1782707231", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/iko/4/blade-banish?utm_source=api", "local": "img/banish/d8838e16-96ca-4f73-ad61-7e98a76c4baf.jpg"}, {"id": "0df450be-9bd2-45be-ae59-fa8d19f6a391", "name": "Dark Banishing", "set": "TPR", "type_line": "Instant", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["B"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/1/4/141dbd31-b813-46da-849e-e13d97dd2e17.jpg?1782750722", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/1/4/141dbd31-b813-46da-849e-e13d97dd2e17.jpg?1782750722", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/tpr/92/dark-banishing?utm_source=api", "local": "img/banish/0df450be-9bd2-45be-ae59-fa8d19f6a391.jpg"}, {"id": "67dec976-bcf5-4995-8da1-cd570862d3cf", "name": "Guardian Naga // Banishing Coils", "set": "CLB", "type_line": "Creature — Snake // Instant — Adventure", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["W"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/1/8/18da890e-0f8d-41e9-a29f-24cb5393c464.jpg?1782701345", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/1/8/18da890e-0f8d-41e9-a29f-24cb5393c464.jpg?1782701345", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/clb/23/guardian-naga-banishing-coils?utm_source=api", "local": "img/banish/67dec976-bcf5-4995-8da1-cd570862d3cf.jpg"}], "flavor_snippets": [{"card": "Skyhunter Skirmisher", "set": "MM2", "html": "&quot;Like dawn&#x27;s first light, blind the unprepared and <mark>banish</mark> the shadows.&quot;\n—Skyhunter creed", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/a/d/adbf772f-ebdf-4c04-996f-0dbf1826049b.jpg?1782750619"}, {"card": "Kin-Tree Severance", "set": "TDM", "html": "&quot;For his crimes—burn his blood and cut him from his ancestors. Perennation is only for family.&quot;\n—Dictate of House Mevak in the <mark>banishment</mark> of Oret", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/b/5/b577e246-3377-42aa-856e-b9fa89f3603a.jpg?1782687152"}, {"card": "Takara", "set": "PVAN", "html": "Takara <mark>banishes</mark> the shadow of her father&#x27;s ignoble reputation through the dedication, plain speaking, and swift action of a warrior. By refusing Starke&#x27;s path of self-interest and opportunism, she has learned what he never will know: the value of sacrifice for a worthy cause.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/7/6/763993dc-edd5-4c1e-a18f-a98cc3ca401d.jpg?1782755487"}, {"card": "Devouring Light", "set": "RVR", "html": "Into the light the good are welcomed, and with the light the evil are <mark>banished</mark>.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/a/8/a81a828b-e17e-4789-b73e-1f44a7f03e9f.jpg?1782731203"}, {"card": "Cloudstone Curio", "set": "RVR", "html": "It *wants* to remain a mystery, <mark>banishing</mark> the curious in favor of less inquisitive company.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/6/1/6146bf98-3cab-4044-a1a2-cf2203f617aa.jpg?1782731030"}, {"card": "Zuko's Exile", "set": "TLA", "html": "As punishment for his disobedience, Zuko was <mark>banished</mark> and sent to capture the Avatar. Only then could he return home with his honor.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/9/0/9090b055-3406-4fed-a8c6-3f6353a9600e.jpg?1782684688"}, {"card": "Dawnstrike Vanguard", "set": "EOE", "html": "&quot;Arrive as the dawn, and <mark>banish</mark> night through your brilliance!&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/5/a/5a041722-9483-469f-9c17-7f0253b0db50.jpg?1782685579"}, {"card": "Rumbling Slum", "set": "HOP", "html": "The Orzhov contract the Izzet to animate slum districts and <mark>banish</mark> them to the wastes. The Gruul adopt them and send them back to the city for vengeance.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/9/d/9d8fd566-0460-4f2f-99c2-8999ce6f2c61.jpg?1782753462"}, {"card": "Carrion Screecher", "set": "GN2", "html": "The <mark>banished</mark> have come home to roost.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/4/5/45a4010d-6a27-4ab5-aff6-e658b39f44b1.jpg?1782744994"}, {"card": "Flayed One", "set": "40K", "html": "Those suspected of carrying the flayer curse are summarily <mark>banished</mark>, lest the corruption spread to other Necrons.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/b/0/b0ab96a5-0bcc-4732-8936-9522f3de3962.jpg?1782700211"}, {"card": "Abandoned Sarcophagus", "set": "C20", "html": "Although long since dead, the <mark>banished</mark> dissenters finally took their vengeance.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/2/3/23b587f3-5eac-45a7-a048-dd73d2a2b74f.jpg?1782707283"}, {"card": "Devout Lightcaster", "set": "ZEN", "html": "&quot;Goddess, grant us light to <mark>banish</mark> the world&#x27;s shadows.&quot;\n—Prayer to Kamsa", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/6/16e31e43-84d3-429e-9e81-60b325989c93.jpg?1782715682"}, {"card": "Merrow Bonegnawer", "set": "EVE", "html": "<mark>Banished</mark> to the Dark Meanders for hideous crimes, some merrows find a taste for the darkness . . . and the dead.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/0/9/09e49aa4-ac23-49b1-b9b7-49d45b56b21d.jpg?1782716057"}, {"card": "Gnottvold Recluse", "set": "KHM", "html": "Fed up with webs impeding travelers in other realms, Kolvori <mark>banished</mark> the giant spiders to Gnottvold, where their webs snare only the occasional rampaging troll.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/a/f/af46c8c8-5dfa-4ebb-b0b9-cd25d01dd432.jpg?1782705445"}], "mechanics_snippets": [{"card": "Grey Knight Paragon", "set": "40K", "html": "Flash\nRites of <mark>Banishment</mark> — When this creature enters, destroy target attacking creature. If that creature is a Demon, exile it instead."}], "thumb": {"art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/a/d/adbf772f-ebdf-4c04-996f-0dbf1826049b.jpg?1782750619", "small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/a/d/adbf772f-ebdf-4c04-996f-0dbf1826049b.jpg?1782750619", "card": "Skyhunter Skirmisher"}}